Simple app playing sounds of a Star Wars lightsaber in 4 variations based on the gyroscope and proximity sensors.

- Start sound
- Idle hum
- Higher when you swing the saber
- Hit sound when swinging fast in one direction or hitting something with the proximity sensor

Lightsaber Sound is open source and licensed under Apache License, Version 2.0.

The sounds are from:
- http://theforce.net/fanfilms/postproduction/soundfx/saberfx_fergo.asp
- http://www.mediacollege.com/downloads/sound-effects/star-wars/lightsaber/